%% Diagram: INP latency phases
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant M as Main thread
    participant R as Renderer

    U->>M: Tap / click / key
    Note over M: Input Delay
    activate M
    Note over M: Processing Time
    deactivate M
    Note over R: Presentation Delay
    R-->>U: Next Paint
